view.name: Traffic speed camera locations
view.description: The location of all red light, fixed, point to point and mobile speed cameras in the ACT.

columns.name: CAMERA TYPE
columns.description: The ACT has a variety of speed cameras. This column displays the particular type of camera used at that location.

columns.name: CAMERA LOCATION CODE
columns.description: A code is assigned to each location. If more than one site is located on the street a letter is added to identify the exact location.

columns.name: LOCATION_CODE
columns.description: A code is assigned to identify each street.

columns.name: LATITUDE
columns.description: Latitude and longitude are combined to give a precise location on a map.

columns.name: LONGITUDE
columns.description: Latitude and longitude are combined to give a precise location on a map.

columns.name: LOCATION DESCRIPTION
columns.description: The street, or cross streets, where the camera is located.
